snippet.title: Crab Champions Variety Update Trailer
snippet.description:
🦀 Full patch notes are available here: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/774801/view/3905248409706008902 🦀

🧊 ABILITIES: GRENADE, GRAPPLING HOOK, LASER BEAM, BLACK HOLE & ICE BLAST

🗡️ MELEE WEAPONS: CLAW, DAGGER & HAMMER

🔫 NEW WEAPONS: LASER CANNONS & SEAGLE

🎲 MINIGAMES: ARCADE, HOLDOUT & DUEL (PvP)

🎉 QUICKPLAY

🎹  NEW CONTENT: MUSIC, LOOT, ENEMIES AND MUCH MORE

💰 BIG BALANCE CHANGES
